    "(9)Thus we have obtained a well-defined non-genuine local operator lying at the end of a line operator.Most importantly, non-genuine operators form a layered structure:1.",
    "We begin with genuine q-dimensional operators, which we denote by O (x) q with the superscript x distinguishing different such operators.",
